snippet.title: Project Lilith - Reveal Trailer
snippet.description:
Add to your wishlist! https://store.steampowered.com/app/1578460/Project_Lilith

Developed by Soro Games

You've been cursed, you've been betrayed. Now it's time for vengeance! Journey through various lands to find your oppressor - Lilith. Be prepared as the journey will be a bloodshed. Kill whatever is in your path to find the ones that destroyed your life!
